192
00:12:29,216 --> 00:12:30,284
Oh, shit.

193
00:12:30,384 --> 00:12:32,853
-Here. Just let me --
-No. I can do it.

194
00:12:32,953 --> 00:12:35,122
-Okay. So if you just get the --
